Setup

library(tidyverse)

usecore <- 4
doParallel::registerDoParallel(usecore)

scale_color <- viridis::scale_color_viridis()
discrete_color <- ggsci::scale_color_d3("category20")

load data

Rawc <- read.table(file="/home/guestA/n70275c/fuji/work/Logireg/data/GSE143437_DeMicheli_MuSCatlas_rawdata.txt", sep="\t", header=T, row.names=1 )
Normc <- read.table(file="/home/guestA/n70275c/fuji/work/Logireg/data/GSE143437_DeMicheli_MuSCatlas_normalizeddata.txt", sep="\t", header=T, row.names=1 ) #scaled data
meta <- read_tsv("/home/guestA/n70275c/fuji/work/Logireg/data/GSE143437_DeMicheli_MuSCatlas_metadata.txt")

data processing

useg <- (rowSums(Normc>0) > 10)
normc <- as_tibble((Normc[useg,]),rownames = "ext_gene")
mat <- scale(t(normc[,-1]),center=FALSE) %>% as.matrix() %>% Matrix::drop0()
